channel.title: Rune-Sleepz Development!
channel.description:
Start Coding Date: 9th June.
1st Coded Item: Was Dragon Claws Also With 4 spec [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/35lhj46.png[/img]
2nd:Added More Npcs To Training Area. [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/TrainingNPCS.jpg[/img]
3rd Added Staff Area (Not DavidScape I Am Not A Leecher) All Coded By Myself. [img]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/StaffArea.jpg?t=1244890880[/img]
4th Added :;Char For All Players: [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/char.jpg[/img]
5th Added Real Runescape Stats On Player Including Wieght. [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/Stats.jpg[/img]
6th Added Staff Cape Only Staff Allow To Wear. Well Its The Cape In The Cape Slot. [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/Stats.jpg[/img] 7th Added The Hitpoint Lady What Was Missing From Errors.
8th Added Real High Scores (Well i am adding Real One online Website) [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/highscores.jpg[/img]
9th Added Full Shops For people When Won Minigame They can spend the 1Mil What they Get. [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/shops.jpg[/img]
10th Added Is Full Skill Cape No Invisable At The End For 2 Seconds [img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/runescape/images/8/88/99defemote.gif[/img]
11th Added The NEW Way To Train Mage And Range.
12th Added Full Wood Cutting No Glicthing (Looking The Other Way) [IMG]http://i600.photobucket.com/albums/tt83/mithscape508help/wc.jpg[/img]
13th Added Full FireMaking Like The Purple Lighters and Blue Lighters Work 100% And After 2 Mins Turns Into Ash.
14th Added A New Way To Train Rune-Craft.
15th 1ST BUBLY SERVER WITH LD And HD. [img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/runescape/images/8/88/99defemote.gif[/img]
16th Added The Wepon Moves on The Dh Like Slash And Stab. [img]http://i33.tinypic.com/jfc96t.gif[/img]
And That Most Of The Development Of Rune-Sleepz.
Sorry For Some Non Pics Cause I was Uploading Them But It Froze I Try Edit It. Please Comment What i Can Improve Thankyou.
Some Credits Go To Matt Coder Of Rune-sleepz
